quran[24]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,91,"àlàáfíà ni fún ọ láààrin àwọn èrò ọwọ́ ọ̀tún."
  56,92,"Ní ti ẹni tí ó bá wà nínú àwọn olùpe-òdodo-nírọ́, àwọn olùṣìnà,"
  56,93,"n̄ǹkan àlejò (wọn) ni omi tó gbóná parí"
  68,25,"Wọ́n jí lọ (sí oko wọn) lórí èrò-ọkàn kan (pé) àwọn lágbára."
  68,26,"Nígbà tí wọ́n rí i, wọ́n wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa ti ṣìnà."
  68,27,"Rárá o, wọ́n ṣe ìkórè oko léèwọ̀ fún wa ni.”"
  69,22,"nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra gíga."
  69,23,"Àwọn èso rẹ̀ (sì) máa wà ní àrọ́wọ́tó."
  69,24,"Ẹ jẹ, kí ẹ sì mu pẹ̀lú ìgbàdún nítorí ohun tí ẹ tì síwájú nínú àwọn ọjọ́ tí ó ti ré kọjá."
  70,16,"Ó máa bó awọ orí tòró."
  70,17,"(Iná) yó máa ké sí ẹni tó kẹ̀yìn sí (ìgbágbọ́ òdodo), tí ó sì takété sí i,"
  70,18,"ó kó (ọrọ̀) jọ, ó sì fi pamọ́ (kò ná an fún ẹ̀sìn)."
  71,13,"Kí ló mu yín tí ẹ kò páyà títóbi Allāhu?"
  71,14,"Ó sì kúkú ṣẹ̀dá yín láti ìrísí kan sí òmíràn (nínú oyún).1 {1}",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, láti ìrísí àtọ̀ sí ìrísí ẹ̀jẹ̀ dídì, lẹ́yìn náà sí bááṣí ẹran.]
  71,15,"Ṣé ẹ kò wòye sí bí Allāhu ṣe dá àwọn sánmọ̀ méje ní ìpele ìpele ni?"
  72,10,"Dájúdájú àwa kò sì mọ̀ bóyá aburú ni wọ́n gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn tó wà lórí ilẹ̀ tàbí Olúwa wọn gbèrò ìmọ̀nà fún wọn."
  72,11,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹni rere wà nínú wa. Àwọn mìíràn yàtọ̀ sí ìyẹn tún wà nínú wa. A wà lójú ọ̀nà (ẹ̀sìn) ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀."
  72,12,"Dájúdájú àwa mọ àmọ̀dájú pé àwa kò lè mórí bọ́ mọ́ Allāhu lọ́wọ́ lórí ilẹ̀. Àwa kò sì lè sá mọ́ Ọn lọ́wọ́."
  73,4,"Tàbí fi kún un. Kí o sì ké al-Ƙur’ān pẹ̀lú pẹ̀lẹ́pẹ̀lẹ́.1 {1}",1:[Ní ìbámu sí āyah yìí, kí ẹnì kan ké odidi al-Ƙur’ān parí láààrin àsìkò díẹ̀ nípasẹ̀ ìkánjú kò lè mú kí onítọ̀ún gbádùn adùn al-Ƙur’ān. Kò sì lè mú ẹ̀san rẹ̀ kún kẹ́kẹ́. Lára oore tí ó rọ̀ mọ́ kíké al-Ƙur’ān pẹ̀lú pẹ̀lẹ́pẹ̀lẹ́ ni pé, ó máa fún wa ní àǹfààní láti rí àwọn lẹ́tà (ìró) rẹ̀ pè dáradára. Ó máa ṣe àlékún àgbọ́yé àti àfọkànsí fún wa. Ìtẹ̀lé àṣẹ Allāhu sì fẹ̀ẹ̀kan ni kíké al-Ƙur’ān pẹ̀lú pẹ̀lẹ́pẹ̀lẹ́.]
  73,5,"Dájúdájú Àwa máa gbé ọ̀rọ̀ tó lágbára fún ọ."
  73,6,"Dájúdájú ìdìde kírun lóru, ó wọnú ọkàn jùlọ, ó sì dára jùlọ fún kíké (al-Ƙur’ān)."
  74,1,"Ìwọ olùdaṣọbora."
  74,2,"Dìde kí o ṣèkìlọ̀."
  74,3,"Olúwa rẹ sì ni kí o gbé títóbi fún."